v&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;css-1ccrm8j&quot;&gt;gatsby 프로젝트 설정파일인 &lt;code class=&quot;css-0&quot;&gt;package.json&lt;/code&gt;의 &lt;code class=&quot;css-0&quot;&gt;script&lt;/code&gt;부분에 다음부분을 추가한다.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;json&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;prism-code language-json&quot; style=&quot;color:#F8F8F2;background-color:#282A36&quot; data-linenumber=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;button type=&quot;button&quot; name=&quot;copy code to clipboard&quot; class=&quot;code-copy-button css-l84w3r&quot;&gt;Copy&lt;span aria-roledescription=&quot;status&quot; class=&quot;css-1gy8470&quot;&gt;copy code to clipboard&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/button&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-json&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;token-line&quot; style=&quot;color:#F8F8F2&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line-number-style&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;scripts&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token plain&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot; style=&quot;color:rgb(248, 248, 242)&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token plain&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;token-line&quot; style=&quot;color:#F8F8F2&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line-number-style&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token plain&quot;&gt;    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;deploy&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token plain&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot; style=&quot;color:rgb(255, 121, 198)&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;gatsby build &amp;amp;&amp;amp; gh-pages -d public -b master&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token plain&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;token-line&quot; style=&quot;color:#F8F8F2&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line-number-style&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token plain&quot;&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot; style=&quot;color:rgb(248, 248, 242)&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot; style=&quot;color:rgb(248, 248, 242)&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;css-1ccrm8j&quot;&gt;해당 내용은 개발용 브랜치에서 &lt;code class=&quot;css-0&quot;&gt;npm run deploy&lt;/code&gt;를 하면 gh-pages가 실행되서, master branch에 빌드가 완료된 배포 직전의 정보가 push 되는 내용이다.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;css-1ccrm8j&quot;&gt;여기까지 실행을 했다면, minimal-blog가 당신이 설정한 github pages로 배포가 되었을 것이다.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;css-1ccrm8j&quot;&gt;이제 gatsby develop 브랜치로 돌아와서 하나씩 수정하면서 커스터마이징하면 된다.
